0030               *--------------------------------------------------------------
0031      6030     kickstart.code1           equ  >6030   ; Uniform aorg entry addr accross banks
0032      6000     kickstart.code2           equ  >6000   ; Uniform aorg entry addr accross banks
0033      0001     rom0_kscan_on             equ  1       ; Use KSCAN in console ROM#0
0034      0000     debug                     equ  0       ; Turn on debugging mode
